@@eThe Forest of Confusion -- As Kowloon Sees It@@N

@@eCourier Lantern Office, Western Anomaly Intelligence@@N

The Forest of Confusion lies north of Kiess -- a western concern,
far from Coppersalt Bay. Kiess deals with the mist incursion, the
failing patrol roads, the contracting reliable perimeter. This is
@@yKiess's problem@@N. Except for two details that make it ours.

First: the @@WSpirebound Conclave@@N. The confusion mists were not
natural -- they were engineered quarantine created by druids to
contain @@lcrystal matrices@@N the Conclave embedded in root systems
and then @@rabandoned@@N. The Courier Lantern Office has extensive files
on the Conclave's negligence pattern. Their resonance crystals in
the Cinderteeth may have amplified the seismic coupling that drove
our @@rAshfall Monsoon@@N. Their instruments here turned a containable
problem into a spreading anomaly. The Conclave's legacy: @@rinstruments
without keepers, running beyond design parameters@@N. Kowloon has
suffered this before.

Second: @@dcrystal contamination@@N. The broken ones -- humanoids
degraded by prolonged crystal exposure -- congregate where quarantine
once held. The Temple Circle reads this with cold recognition.
Volcanic contamination degraded our water. Crystal contamination
degrades minds and the boundary between living and landscape.
@@rDifferent poison, same institutional negligence at the source.@@N

The druidic order maintaining the mists died demographically. Without
maintenance, mists lost calibrated purpose and diffused outward. The
Courier Lantern Office marks this as @@ysuccession failure@@N: knowledge
in too few hands, lost when the last keeper died. Our signal network
is designed against this. Every relay protocol documented in three
locations. Every lamp-keeper trains a successor before the @@dAshfall
Vigil@@N. @@yWe do not allow single points of knowledge failure.@@N

@@gTreants@@N guard as sentinels. @@eCentaurs@@N maintain armed neutrality.
@@rNeogi@@N exploit the fog. @@rYmmas@@N holds a fortified cabin root growth
has never reclaimed. The Wardens file these under @@dwestern threat
profiles@@N -- not immediate, but relevant if mist incursion spreads.

Three institutions failed in sequence: the Conclave created the
problem, the druids contained it, Kiess manages symptoms. The Jade
Magistracy's assessment: @@ythis is what happens when containment is
treated as solution@@N. Kowloon does not contain problems. We @@yname
them, light them, and maintain the watch@@N.
